/*****************
Set to create Package.json
********************/
**NodeJs must be install
> Navigate to the folder using cmd/termianl
> npm init
> answer all question
> type 'yes'



Node Package Manager

/******
Local Dependency/Package/Node_Module
> Installed in one folder

Global Dependency/Package/Node_Module
> System Dependency
> Generate
> Start
> Run
*******/


/*****
Step to install local Dependency
****/
> Navigate to the folder using cmd/termianl
> npm install <Packagename>/ npm i <Packagename>/ 

/*****
Step to install Global Dependency
****/

#Win
> Open cmd as admin
> npm i -g @aakashdeveloper/create-node-app

#Mac 
> Open terminal
> sudo npm i -g @aakashdeveloper/create-node-app


/*****
Step to create react application
****/

#Win
> Open cmd as admin
> npm i -g create-react-app
> Navigate to the folder using cmd
> create-react-app <appname>
> cd appname
> npm start

#Mac/linux
> Open terminal
> sudo npm i -g create-react-app
> Navigate to the folder using termianl
> create-react-app <appname>
> cd appname
> npm start



